data.description: This beautiful, well-maintained home, nestled on a cul de sac, offers new luxury vinyl flooring, a freshly painted kitchen, new lighting fixtures, and updates throughout.  The lower level family room offers a wood-burning fireplace, 1/2 bath, and a walk-out to the park-like backyard. The warmer weather will be here soon and the backyard is perfect for entertaining with a newly constructed patio, stone fire pit, privacy fence, and new pool liner. Roof, Furnace, and Hot water tank are 10 years or less. The lower level laundry room includes washer and dryer and spacious storage.
